title: SignerKeyType
description:
SignerKeyType is an XDR Enum defines as:

```text enum SignerKeyType { SIGNER_KEY_TYPE_ED25519 = KEY_TYPE_ED25519, SIGNER_KEY_TYPE_PRE_AUTH_TX = KEY_TYPE_PRE_AUTH_TX, SIGNER_KEY_TYPE_HASH_X = KEY_TYPE_HASH_X, SIGNER_KEY_TYPE_ED25519_SIGNED_PAYLOAD = KEY_TYPE_ED25519_SIGNED_PAYLOAD }; ```
